<HEADLINE> Petacchi Wins 12th Stage in Tour of Spain Cycle Race </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MADRID, September 7 (Xinhua) -- Italian Alessandro Petacchi of
the Fasso Bortolo team won the 12th stage of the Tour of Spain
cycle race on Thursday, a 131.5 kilometers ride around Zaragoza.
</P>
<P>
Spaniard Angel Casero riding for the Festina team retained the
overall leader's gold jersey. 
</P>
</TEXT>
