<HEADLINE> First South Asian Wushu Championship Ends in Nepal </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KATHMANDU, September 8 (Xinhua) -- The first South Asian Wushu
Championship, the largest kind of the traditional Chinese martial
arts competition, concluded here on Friday, with Nepal snatching
23 of the 28 gold medals.
