<HEADLINE> Art Creation Center Set for Improving Film Quality </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 8 (Xinhua) -- The Chinese Film Group set up
an art creation center in Beijing today, marking the beginning of
the reforming of China's leading film group.
</P>
<P>
Consisting of the Beijing Film Studio, Chinese Children's Film
Studio, Chinese Film Co-operation Studio and Chinese Film Company,
the Chinese Film Group is the biggest film enterprise in China.
</P>
<P>
The Art Creation Center is the first institution set up by the
group, but will be followed by a movie and television studio, a
movie and television base, a training center and an administration
center for retirees in the film industry.
</P>
<P>
