<HEADLINE> China Awards 60 Senior Professors </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 8 (Xinhua) -- As the 16th Teachers' Day,
which falls on September 10, draws near, China today granted
awards to 60 senior professors with glorious academic achievements.
</P>
<P>
The awarding drive was sponsored by the China Senior Professors
' Association. Chinese Vice Premier Li Lanqing delivered his
congratulations to the 60 award-winners.
</P>
