recovered previous losses as buying interest picked up this week.
</P>
<P>
The Shenzhen B-share index wound up the week's trade higher at
121.00 points while the weekly turnover contracted to 477.14
million HK dollars, a shortfall of 121.83 million HK dollars from
the previous week's total.
