for a visit, also met with President of the Serbian Republic of
Yugoslavia Milan Milutinovic and his Yugoslav counterpart Zivadin
Jovanovic.
</P>
<P>
He told Jovanovic that Greece is willing to develop ties with
Yugoslavia and will support the lifting of sanctions imposed on
Yugoslavia. 
