<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 8 (Xinhua) -- A new residential area to
house professors of China's most prestigious Beijing and Qinghua
universities has been completed right before China's Teacher's Day,
which will fall on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
More than 1,000 professors, including 100 members of the
Chinese Academy of Sciences and the Chinese Academy of Engineering
will move into the new houses near Qinghua University in northern
Beijing.
